prepunc " 236
postpunc " 356
always \s-" 36-36-356
always \s-ÔÇØ 36-36-356
always ..." 3-3-3-356
always ÔÇª" 3-3-3-356
always ...ÔÇØ 3-3-3-356
always ÔÇªÔÇØ 3-3-3-356
always ?" 236-356
word " 236
