# Remove U+200C three-per-em space = thick space but let it be a virtual space.
space \x200C 9							# Assign x200C to virtual dot 9. [Peter Engstr├Âm 2011-03-23]
noback pass2 @9 ?						# Remove virtual dot 9 during second pass. [Peter Engstr├Âm 2011-03-23]
space \x00a0 a
include spaces.uti

